A&P Contractors has purchased a property to be used in connection with A&P's Construction Inc's construction business since 1974.  A Use and Occupancy was issued.  In 1959 staff of MNCPPC write that there were several dwellings with a sheet metal shop at the rear of one of the residences.

This property constitutes what is left of the property that was for many years a landscaping business on Norbeck Road.  Pieces of the property were sold in 2010 & 2011.  A portion of the property was left however was separated from the piece of the property on which the house sits by Norbeck Road.  That piece was used by the owners of the property until they sold property and house.  The piece across Norbeck Rd will be used for landscaping property.
